highlights.text: XXXTENTACION has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Arms Around You (feat. Maluma & Swae Lee)” is the highest at #20.
“Santa Baby” by Kylie Minogue is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 48 spots at #148.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 104 weeks straight.
“imagine” by Ariana Grande is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #8.
